data.description: History lovers line up to view this charming turn of the century colonial home in Old Town Suffolk. Total of 4 bedrooms. One bedroom and full bathroom downstairs, 3 bedrooms and one and half bathrooms upstairs. This homes kitchen has been updated with new tile flooring, new cabinets/sink, new refrigerator and NEW granite counter tops! The rest of the home boasts a new HVAC unit with accompanying duct work, fresh paint throughout, hardwood floors and a brand new hot water heater. Don't miss this piece of history, schedule your showing before its gone!
